{"tid":1115880,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街M記個桶雞餐跟得兩包泰式辣醬","createTime":"2019-04-19T13:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T04:56:06.000Z","uid":58659,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7e93c342136d61b96cefbb3bc6abc3cf36d69012","tid":1115880,"uid":58659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"仆佢地個街！岩先同囡囡去油塘m記買16件桶雞餐，發生以下咁既事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我囡囡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：職員<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哥哥仔<br />\n<br />\n當我地俾撚完錢等拎既時候，發覺佢地無俾泰式辣醬我地，咪問個職員拎囉！<br />\n我：唔該，有無泰式辣醬？<br />\n職員：（拎左兩包放入個外賣袋到）<br />\n我囡囡：平時普通餐四件or散叫2件都跟一包，16件得兩包？<br />\n職員：係得兩包.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然之後我地問多次真係得兩包？個職員都好堅持唔再俾，咁都算....咪轉身走人費時爭吵，<br />\n但就同女友一路行一路討論一路屌，跟得兩包真係太過份！<br />\n<br />\n當我地行到屋企樓下仲屌緊果時，有位哥哥仔忍唔住行上黎拍我膊頭<br />\n<br />\n哥哥仔：um.....其實頭先我排你地後面，都係買桶雞餐，我唔食辣醬架，不如俾埋你地丫<br />\n<br />\n我當堂打個突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有同個哥哥仔講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到咁樣俾佢終結話題<br />\n（勿相認哥哥仔)<br />\n<br />\n而家一路食緊一路打呢篇野<br />\n唉. 啲薯條仲要淋過廚師啲雞蛋仔<br />\n冚家剷！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZkTJ6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZkTJ6a.png&h=500efdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e85fd5ee4814caa89651615fa48a6ff3236ed38c","tid":1115880,"uid":28599,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"無可能！我買包薯條叫佢俾包泰式辣醬都照俾<br />\n係咪你樣柒好恰？"},{"pid":"a70d44b878768d2d019adbb535a207ea9e9ba447","tid":1115880,"uid":41602,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"e85fd5ee4814caa89651615fa48a6ff3236ed38c","tid":1115880,"uid":28599,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"無可能！我買包薯條叫佢俾包泰式辣醬都照俾<br />\n係咪你樣柒好恰？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"而家好似要俾一蚊喎"},{"pid":"fedde044f8cdc153ddb8ea275d77a516d0e026ee","tid":1115880,"uid":21707,"like":9,"dislike":22,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:42:33.000Z","msg":"啲公仔有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c61b49c2277b879c9043893cdd1e67acfc98fb","tid":1115880,"uid":156133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"你同你囡囡去買M記做咩又彈咗個女友出嚟？"},{"pid":"a18146c0a306f96638b99753009e4370a513924a","tid":1115880,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a70d44b878768d2d019adbb535a207ea9e9ba447","tid":1115880,"uid":41602,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"e85fd5ee4814caa89651615fa48a6ff3236ed38c","tid":1115880,"uid":28599,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"無可能！我買包薯條叫佢俾包泰式辣醬都照俾<br />\n係咪你樣柒好恰？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"而家好似要俾一蚊喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"專搵啲毒撚職員拎 洗鬼俾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f58a2cae0518f9d46d8743c0abf30b95e7d519","tid":1115880,"uid":249510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:13:36.000Z","msg":"琴晚食L完 得果一包 多謝哂"},{"pid":"66cec6ff714b8bfc1c275064bb4bfb821f433199","tid":1115880,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a18146c0a306f96638b99753009e4370a513924a","tid":1115880,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a70d44b878768d2d019adbb535a207